Ouman EH-203 serial registers
```
01 (0x01) - device identity and version
f9c6980032303300d74a616e20323620313000000000000000000000000000
f9c69800 - serial number (le int)
32303300 - model (ascii)
d7 - version (divide by 10)
4a616e203236203130 - build date (ascii)

02 (0x02) - clock
07e80208162005
07e8 - year (le int)
02 - month
08 - day
16 - hour
20 - minute
05 - second

03 (0x03) - same clock as 02, duplicate for some reason?

04-11 (0x04-0x0b) all zero, maybe schedule programs?

12 (0x0c) - L1 settings
```
